s/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩個大黨唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n話明大黨 緊係係旁邊吶喊助威 之後係FB大叫議會不公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd66d600100a5449561b5a56dca8911d5beb360e","tid":471430,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T09:25:19.000Z","msg":"白生打鳩佢 佢還拖就變台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515ba065a0b3c3a19e7ddc55c739af150002cad4","tid":471430,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解我覺得泛民好似只係得慢必一個開會咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有朱都有幫手既<br />\n其他既真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}